snippet.title: Chinese Takeout! Fighting Game Trailer
snippet.description:
The Shaolin Express is the greatest restaurant in Chinatown. But the notorious gang known as the Kung Fu Hustlers came and steal all of their secret recipes. It's up to Kung Pow, Head Chef & Kung Fu master, to fight her way through various thugs to get them back!

Play the game HERE : http://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/658621

Download HERE: http://www.rocketbrown.com/
 
Theme song by Sean Marshall
